Titolo: Aliens: Fireteam Elite

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: Aliens: Fireteam Elite is a 2021 multiplayer third-person shooter game developed by Cold Iron Studio in collaboration with Disney's 20th Century Games. It is a standalone sequel to the original Alien trilogy. In contrast to Alien: Isolation, Fireteam Elite is more in line with Aliens: Colonial Marines, and focuses on action rather than survival-horror. The game is a third-person co-op shooter, able to be played with friends or AI teammates.

